Due to its high expected accuracy, the development of a single or multiple ion nuclear clock can be considered as the ultimate goal. However, it is also the most experimentally demanding, as it will require driving nuclear Rabi oscillations of individual laser-cooled 229\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
