				\begin{document}$$^{229\text {m}}$$\end{document}Th followed by hyperfine spectroscopy of the electronic shell to monitor excitation of the isomeric state provides the basis of the nuclear clock proposal [258]. It is the objective of all groups that are planning to develop a nuclear clock based on individual 229\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
