				\begin{document}$$^{229\text {m}}$$\end{document}Th energy to a value above the ionization threshold of neutral thorium [12], direct laser cooling of triply ionized 229\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
