				\begin{document}$$^{229}$$\end{document}Th in a Paul trap [57], direct detection of the isomer’s internal conversion (IC) decay channel [398], the determination of the isomer’s IC lifetime [319], investigation of the 229m\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
